Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total duration from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Minimum duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases where it directly precedes 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that involve 'Completed + In Call' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across different organizational countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Duration comparison of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' when followed by 'Accepted + Assigned' vs. 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that were completed within the same day vs. cases that spanned multiple days
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum waiting time before 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' is initiated after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average lead time to start 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' after any 'Completed' activity
Metric: the average of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Resolved' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Closed' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Earliest start time of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Latest completion time of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' during the first quarter of the year vs. the last quarter of the year
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
